1 Administration and Federal Transit Administration
2 contracts; and
3 (11) establish consumer protection standards with regard to
4 subscriptions to community energy facilities.
5 (c) In addition to rules adopted under subsection (b), the
6 commission may adopt any other rules the commission considers
7 appropriate or necessary for the administration of this chapter,
8 including rules regarding the following:
9 (1) The maximum proportion that the total nameplate
